(124, 'Land travel to Davao, anyone?', '<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Travelers can now visit Davao City via Bus! Yep, you read that right! PITX  is now mounting daily trips to Davao City service by the Davao Metro Shuttle. A one-way fare will cost you P3,680. For those who enjoy a long and scenic drive, this three-day, two-night journey over land and sea may suit your travel lifestyle.</span>', '', '2022-10-12 09:12:41', '2022-10-12 09:17:13', NULL),
(134, 'Megawide, PH1 break ground for Ortigas Hills Project', '<div class=\"ewa-rteLine\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Calibri, Thonburi, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yi Baiti&quot;, &quot;Javanese Text&quot;; font-size: 1px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18pt;\">Extraordinary developer PH1 World Developers and Megawide Construction Corp. have started the construction of the Ortigas Hills Project in Taytay, Rizal following a groundbreaking ceremony held in August.</span></div><div class=\"ewa-rteLine\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Calibri, Thonburi, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yi Baiti&quot;, &quot;Javanese Text&quot;; font-size: 1px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18pt;\"> </span></div><div class=\"ewa-rteLine\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Calibri, Thonburi, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yi Baiti&quot;, &quot;Javanese Text&quot;; font-size: 1px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18pt;\">The project, Megawide’s third venture in the municipality, consists of three mid-rise condominium buildings in a 16,470 sq m. property in Ortigas Extension, Brgy. San Isidro, Taytay, Rizal. The Ortigas Hills Project will boast PH1’s promise of Extra Space at No Extra Cost, through its exclusive AddLoft Technology.</span></div>', '', '2022-10-12 09:14:33', '2022-10-12 09:15:31', '2022-10-12 09:15:31'),
