(161, 'Happy 4th anniversary, PITX!', '<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW29389560 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW29389560 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW29389560 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW29389560 BCX8\" paraid=\"1780527976\" paraeid=\"{44d9df2c-2d92-4eb0-ab25-c3daa3b9d4de}{156}\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#202020\" face=\"Helvetica\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica;\">PITX celebrated its fourth-year anniversary, with the theme: \"4 EveryJuan\" which aimed to give its passengers the First-World experience through its landport.  \r\n  \r\nPart of the celebration was a contest called \"Lakwatsa 4 EveryJuan\" which ran from December 2 to 16, 2022, in which more than 300 passengers joined through purchasing P 100 within the terminal and submitted these receipts to the Customer Information Desk in exchange for a coupon.   \r\n  \r\nAround 100 passengers won prizes through partnerships with Love Radio, GCash, SMART, Ceres, Bicol Isarog, Jac Liner - Solid North, Yellow Cab, Krispy Kreme, Wendy\'s, Subway, and Mocz Drivi