(165, 'MBody Project: The journey to fitness starts now!', '<div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">It\'s not too late to lose weight!&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">March is all about staying active and fit as the Learning and Talent Management (LTM) team of Corporate Human Resources launched this year’s “MBody Project” for the employees of Megawide Corporate and sister companies, PH1 and Citicore, last February 17.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">The fitness sessions, which will run from March 1 to May 31, focus on core and cardio trainings with supplementary dietary advices. From basic workouts to advanced workouts, the fitness project provides employees the opportunity to achieve their fitness goals to stay healthy and fit.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">During the launch, Mark Niro, one of the fitness coaches, emphasized the importance of workouts, especially for employees who spend most of the time sitting.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">“Regular exercise is very important for sedentary people as it helps reduce the risks of obesity, diabetes, and heart diseases. This also helps improve mood and energy levels which can boost one’s self-esteem and confidence,” he shared.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">Employees who are able to complete most of the sessions will receive welcome kit items such as towels, mats, water bottles, and smart watches.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span><br></div><div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">Don’t forget to join the MBody Project Viber Community by scanning the QR code above!</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Helvetica\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></font></div><font face=\"Helvetica\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Here are some video highlights:</span></font><br><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HLD.HRPublic/Edp9_TsH29dNl0PCv3m5qEEBmvlxNOlBq6dPxn_0GbeVIw?e=rtGKzv\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">MBody Project</span></a></div></div><div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HLD.HRPublic/EdFff5wm3AVLoxawyy0D2H8BkwbxzyUbkpk-KxHzy_M7Qw?e=GfEYYe\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">MBody Project 2</span></a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HLD.HRPublic/EavqowIngCZFnrXEOohMASwBwX2f8Wyda-7BRE46sToUGg?e=JiZT74\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HLD.HRPublic/EavqowIngCZFnrXEOohMASwBwX2f8Wyda-7BRE46sToUGg?e=JiZT74\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">MBody Project 3</span></a><br></div></div>', NULL, '2023-03-13 04:10:15', '2023-03-14 07:08:33', NULL),
