(187, 'Emergency? Megawide’s ready!', '<div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">As part of disaster resilience and readiness, Megawide Corporate, PH1 World Developers and Citicore Power conducted an earthquake drill last April 27 in Santolan Town Plaza.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;\">The alarm was activated at 8:44am and employees quickly managed to secure their safety. The drill was participated and audited by Bureau of Fire Protection (BFP), San Juan led by SF01 Arnel Abrera and F02 Diana Carlos to check the emergency awareness, preparedness and responsiveness not only of the employees but most importantly, the&nbsp; Megawide Emergency Response Team.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">Led by CMT Director Jason Torres, the Megawide Emergency Response Team believes that this kind of activities will further strengthen the company’s overall emergency response vital to the business’ operations and continuity. </span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">Watch the videos here!<br></span><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/EeaaNPyiWBpPsy62qPm7nGUBU177wtFBrszJItgIZj3rTg?e=scOc4t\" target=\"_blank\">search and rescue</a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/EdRHu60JnD1GlSxdumUSeLoBWB9nXKhGG2B9_cETDsiPew?e=4cTLjt\" target=\"_blank\">search and rescue 2</a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/EYJ5NDv8_mpJlBrt6h3mo-8B1pVH8N9QDk8qvkLhfvUQTw?e=x88zq9\" target=\"_blank\">evacuation</a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/EW7yVQ0n-BtEsldYjdaHsJAB9j2iyTXT7-1JtmL1LgDPfQ?e=Yvc3mi\" target=\"_blank\">evacuation 2</a><br><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:v:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/Ec4wa45XiutGmL7XXMNlw5UBg64gZGmGimMMPoD8GT5zOA?e=Xj9JTD\" target=\"_blank\">assembly</a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://megawideph.sharepoint.com/:i:/s/HoldCo.HRInitiatives-101HoldCoAdminandFMD/EbfagRXTIPdLj2yhVDYMMlkBra5q5vZ2sftl_5lnm0tAxQ?e=6ejwri\" target=\"_blank\">assembly 2</a><br><br><br><br><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div>', NULL, '2023-05-12 01:50:04', '2023-05-12 02:12:57', NULL),
(188, 'Discover the newest food hub in Cebu!', '<div><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;\">A new food hub called The Barracks was soft-launched on May 1 in Carbon.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;\">Dubbed as Cebu\'s first \"hawker center,\" The Barracks offers a variety of local food offerings, such as lechon, grilled foods, bread and pastries, and other Cebuano food favorites.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">The Barracks is so named for its historic location, formerly the Warwick Barracks, which was once a military garrison during the American occupation.&nbsp;</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;\">The grand launch is scheduled for May 12, 2023.&nbsp;</span></div>', NULL, '2023-05-12 02:17:56', '2023-05-12 02:17:56', NULL),
(189, 'Way to go, scholars!', '<p style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Megawide</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Foundation proud</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ly</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> announce</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\">s</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-variant-ligatures: none; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> the </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW66961558 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit